  <title>Quaternions</title>

  <introduction>
    <p> Don't be afraid! Quaternions are just helpful little creatures that love to rotate things. 
    They are made by the intersection of two planes passing through the origin. That gives you the axis of rotation.
      </p>
  </introduction>

